race.comment: Competitive. BAZABALL REWARDED (5) peaks off three comfortable wins here and keeps improving. Has been heavily bet and will get every chance to run out the longer sprint. BATTLE OF THE ICE (4) resumes off an easy Kyneton Maiden win on debut. The jumpouts have been sharp and he has to be kept safe. RECON (2) would be very competitive at best and at his only second-up outing he won easily. Has to be considered as well. TWISTED QUEEN (10) scored in the lone fresh attempt and won the latest trial so keep safe.
